// Windows resource script — embeds the application icon into embrace.exe.
// Compiled with rc.exe (part of the MSVC toolchain) into embrace.res and linked
// into the executable; see tools/win-build.bat. The lowest icon ID becomes the
// icon Windows Explorer / the taskbar shows for the .exe file itself.
// (The runtime window icon is set separately from embrace-logo.png at startup.)
1 ICON "embrace-logo.ico"
